profile:
We are a licensed and insured business----
Specializing in shower systems, full bath, kitchen,  tile, and other general material installations. All labor and materials meet and exceed ANSI Ontario standards

Macaw Development
*Free estimation
*Demolition & full cleanup + disposal
* Full bathroom renovations
* Entire KITCHENS!! GREYWALL & IKEA PRO INSTALLERS
*All sorts of tile & flooring material - Ceramic, Porcelain, Marble, Travertine, Subway, Mosaic, Metal, Laminate installation
*Repairs
*DIVERSE !!!- We work with multiple brands giving you the best within your budget. Schluter , Wedi, Laticrete, Ardex and tons more.
*Professional advice and installation for a happy customer

We are servicing the GTA area
